casebody.data:
Troy MARTIN, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
ELEVENTH JUDICIAL CIRCUIT, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D16-1003 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. NOVEMBER 21, 2017 ROTHENBERG, C.J., and EMAS and LUCK, JJ., concur.

Upon the Court's own motion, it is ordered that this appeal from the Circuit Court for Miami-Dade County, Florida is dismissed for failure to comply with this Court's order dated November 1, 2017, and with the Florida Rules of Appellate Procedure.
